Title: Integration with On-Premises Data Sources in Azure Synapse Analytics | Developer Support
Description: Orrin Edenfield explores the integration of on-premises data sources in Azure Synapse Analytics. Today many organizations are cloud hybrid in nature so they need to read from and write to on-premises data stores including file systems and relational databases. In this video I show you how to connect to on-premises file systems and relational databases (like Azure SQL Database Edge) using the Integration Pipelines capabilities of Azure Synapse Analytics and the self-hosted integration runtime.
